videos.headline: Texas A&M's Ford rushes in for early TD
videos.description: Texas A&M running back Keith Ford gets the handoff and rushes seven yards for an early touchdown against Kansas State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas A&M's Ford rushes in for early TD) 2016/12/28

videos.headline: Kansas State's Pringle sprints 79 yards for touchdown
videos.description: Kansas State's Byron Pringle catches the deep ball and sprints past the Texas A&M defense for a 79-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Kansas State defense comes up with the interception
videos.description: Trevor Knight pass intercepted Kendall Adams return for no gain to the KanSt 43

videos.headline: Kansas State's Ertz keeps it himself for 5-yard TD
videos.description: Kansas State's Jesse Ertz keeps the ball himself, stiff arms a Texas A&M defender en route to scoring a 5-yard touchdown in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Kansas State's Heath speeds down sidelines for 52-yard TD
videos.description: Kansas State's Dominique Heath gets the handoff and sprints past the Texas A&M defense to score a 52-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kansas State's Heath speeds down sidelines for 52-yard TD) 2016/12/28

videos.headline: Aggies WR with the reception after ball hits teammate in the helmet
videos.description: Trevor Knight pass complete to Christian Kirk for 23 yds to the TexAM 33 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: A&M's Reynolds leaps over defender to make TD catch
videos.description: Texas A&M's Josh Reynolds soars over a Kansas State defender to make a 4-yard touchdown grab in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Ertz gets over the goal line to extend Kansas State's lead
videos.description: Kansas State's Jesse Ertz gets the push to barely get the ball over the goal line for a 1-yard touchdown to give the Wildcats a 33-21 lead over Texas A&M.

videos.headline: Knight finds Reynolds for another A&M touchdown
videos.description: Texas A&M's Josh Reynolds gets the defender to bite on a move and catches the Trevor Knight pass for a 15-yard touchdown in the fourth quarter for their second scoring connection of the game.

videos.headline: Knight can't convert on fourth-and-8
videos.description: With Texas A&M down 33-28 and on fourth-and-8, Trevor Knight can't complete a pass to Damion Ratley, turning the ball back over to Kansas State.

videos.headline: Ertz accounts for 3 TDs in Kansas State's win over Texas A&M
videos.description: Kansas State quarterback Jesse Ertz throws for a 79-yard touchdown and rushes in two others in a 33-28 win against Texas A&M in the Valero V100 Texas Bowl.
